index_terms: CHICAGO MILWAUKEE ST PAUL PACIFIC RAILROAD
summary: An Ordinance of the City of Seattle authorizing the execution and delivery of a deed from the City of Seattle to the Chicago, Milwaukee and St. Paul Railway Company of Washington of the eat one hundred twenty (120) feet of lots twenty-one (21) and twenty-two (22), block three hundred thirty-five (335), Seattle Tide Lands, in exchange for a deed to the City of Seattle of lots one (1) and two (2), block three hundred thirty-seven (337), Seattle Tide Lands, to be used as a site for a fire engine house.
